PublicRemarks: LOOKING FOR GREAT TENANTS AS OF MAY 1.  Rent this new lower level 2 bedroom apartment close to parks, schools, transit, LRT station, St. Laurent Mall, lots of shopping and great eateries...and only 8 minutes to downtown! Recently completed, this rental boasts porcelain floors throughout (with radiant in-floor heating), almost 10 foot ceilings, large windows, in-unit laundry, gorgeous kitchen with gas range, quartz counters, breakfast bar, lots of cabinets and ample counter space, a bright living room with ceiling fan and a 4 piece bathroom. Rental comes with 1 parking spot and access to backyard patio. IDEAL RENTAL for young professionals, mature students or down-sizers. Credit Report, Rental Application and 2 recent pay stubs will be required to apply. Refrigerator, Gas Stove, Dishwasher, Hood Fan, Washer, Dryer all included. Rent is $1800/M + utilities, which on average will be about $90-$110/month. This apartment is bright and ready to move in! INTERIOR PHOTOS ARE OF A SIMILAR UNIT. (27840856)

PublicRemarks: **BRAND NEW- Appliances included** Looking for an affordable bachelor to call home? Welcome to B-130 Carllion, a freshly constructed apartment showcasing top-tier designer finishes and impeccable craftsmanship. Nestled just a few steps from the Rideau River walking and biking trails, as well as proximity to all shopping, amenities, the University of Ottawa, major transit, and downtown, this residence offers an ideal location! The unit features an open-concept living and dining area that transitions to the bed space which includes built in storage. A designer kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, a stove, sleek push-to-open cabinets, quartz countertops, and ample counter and storage space. Affordable street parking permits are available. Tenants are responsible for hydro and gas expenses. (27785683)
